{"tid":975988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【《國歌法》入校】「指示」入中小學 國際校須學唱","createTime":"2019-01-10T05:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T15:25:48.000Z","uid":20058,"like":15,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"77ed7afeedb7fde3c3d22ba8812a578c6bfd1c2e","tid":975988,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"【《國歌法》入校】「指示」入中小學 國際校須學唱 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2TCBXax\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TCBXax&d=NJS9iWJNrGuYhPFqm1V0FGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ef1349b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2TCBXax</a><br />\n<br />\n政府提出《#國歌條例草案》第9條建議，教育局局長須就把《國歌法》納入小學及中學教育發出指示，使學生學習唱國歌、教育學生國歌的歷史、精神及奏唱國歌的禮儀。國際學校及特殊學校亦包括在內，並不論其資助模式及課程。被問到 #國際學校 不同國籍的學生為何要學唱 #中國國歌，聶德權說，任何地方都需要認識當地文化歷史，尊重當地的國家象徵、標誌是「很自然、容易理解」的事。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n《信報》+《信報月刊》合併訂閱優惠送您《不怕老退化》電子書 <br />\n了解更多﹕<a href=\"http://bit.ly/ejfdncom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fejfdncom&d=NJS9iWJNrGuYhPFqm1V0FGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0ac6f7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/ejfdncom</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #今日信報 #國歌法 #小學 #中學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbcee7fba548990991c730cfce2074e6e39eef0","tid":975988,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4114ade1b0c28f231e205e09d9942edc9d2ba9","tid":975988,"uid":2419,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"國際學校都要唱 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d7675be475b1bca97e177c78826a3c930ad9d4","tid":975988,"uid":152476,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"5e4114ade1b0c28f231e20